Command - Class in worldofzuul
Holds information regarding the command typed in by the user, the information is in two parts, the command word of the type CommandWord (an enum) and a second word of the type String.
Command(CommandWord, String) - Constructor for class worldofzuul.Command
The constructor for the class, it simply stores the two parameters parsend in
CommandWord - Enum in worldofzuul
An enum class.
CommandWords - Class in worldofzuul
This class is used to hold the handles to each CommandWord object (the enum)
CommandWords() - Constructor for class worldofzuul.CommandWords
Constructor, it creates a HashMap, as defined above, and then it loops through each valid CommandWord (the enum to contain all of the recognized cmds) It puts the recognized commands into the HashMap The for each loop is used to put each command's object into the HashMap, so that the handle to object can always be retrieved
Conversation - Class in worldofzuul
A new object of conversation gets created everytime a player meets an NPC This handles all of the question and answers the question has To create the conversation, you need to read the equivalent JSON file The creation of a conversation is done in the method "createWholeConversation" and therefore not in the constructor
